#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.vdot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.vdot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:1 of
msgid "Return the dot product of two vectors."
msgstr "返回两个向量的点积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:3 of
msgid ""
"The vdot(`a`, `b`) function handles complex numbers differently than "
"dot(`a`, `b`).  If the first argument is complex the complex conjugate of"
" the first argument is used for the calculation of the dot product."
msgstr ""
"vdot(`a`, `b`) 函数对复数的处理方式与 dot(`a`, `b`) 不同。如果第一个参数"
"是复数，则在计算点积时使用第一个参数的复共轭。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:7 of
msgid ""
"Note that `vdot` handles multidimensional tensors differently than `dot`:"
" it does *not* perform a matrix product, but flattens input arguments to "
"1-D vectors first. Consequently, it should only be used for vectors."
msgstr ""
"注意，`vdot` 对多维张量的处理方式与 `dot` 不同：它*不*执行矩阵乘法，而是"
"先将输入参数展平为一维向量。因此，它只能用于向量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:11 of
msgid ""
"If `a` is complex the complex conjugate is taken before calculation of "
"the dot product."
msgstr "如果 `a` 是复数，则在计算点积前取其复共轭。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:14 of
msgid "Second argument to the dot product."
msgstr "点积的第二个参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:17 of
msgid ""
"**output** -- Dot product of `a` and `b`.  Can be an int, float, or "
"complex depending on the types of `a` and `b`."
msgstr ""
"**output** -- `a` 和 `b` 的点积。根据 `a` 和 `b` 的类型，可以是 int、"
"float 或 complex。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`dot`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:24 of
msgid ""
"Return the dot product without using the complex conjugate of the first "
"argument."
msgstr "返回点积，但不使用第一个参数的复共轭。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:27 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.vdot.vdot:37 of
msgid "Note that higher-dimensional arrays are flattened!"
msgstr "注意，高维数组会被展平！"

